node.text: @inayah worked her ass off while pregnant. I told her to take time for herself and she did that too but still was locked in. I don’t know how we pulled this off but we damn sure did and it’s special!  To all the women out there who are raising families and working at the highest level, I salute you all!  #SideA

node.text: Even worth he threat of a hurricane tens of thousands came and packed out MetLife Stadium. Our first Summer Jam was a success. When the whole stadium started singing In My Bed I almost shed a tear I was so proud of the consistent work @rotimi has been putting in. Thank you @tttorrez @hot97 , This is a big week. His album drops Friday and it’s the best work he’s done to date. I can’t wait for the world to hear it. Let’s fuckin go!!!!! You ain’t gotta respect us but you will respect this hustle 💪🏾💪🏾💪🏾😎

node.text:
Thanks to my friends @amfriendsipo I’m apart of the bedtime and lullaby summer reading series!  Click the link in my bio to register when we go live August 15th!  Shabbat Shalom!
#TheMouseWhoDancedTheHora
